{"entries":[{"id":"scofield-1sa-1-23","title":"1 Samuel 1:23","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":1,"verseStart":23,"chapterEnd":1,"verseEnd":23},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-3-intro","title":"1 Samuel 3 — Chapter Introduction","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":3,"verseStart":0,"chapterEnd":8,"verseEnd":0},"content":"<p><milestone</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-3-4","title":"1 Samuel 3:4","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":3,"verseStart":4,"chapterEnd":3,"verseEnd":4},"content":"<p>Philistines Cf. 1 Samuel 31:3-5 (See Scofield \"1 Samuel 31:3\")</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-4-17","title":"1 Samuel 4:17","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":4,"verseStart":17,"chapterEnd":4,"verseEnd":17},"content":"<p>trust (See Scofield \"Psalms 2:12\") .</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-6-1","title":"1 Samuel 6:1","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":6,"verseStart":1,"chapterEnd":6,"verseEnd":1},"content":"<p>fear (See Scofield \"Psalms 19:9\") .</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-7-17","title":"1 Samuel 7:17","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":7,"verseStart":17,"chapterEnd":7,"verseEnd":17},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-10-8","title":"1 Samuel 10:8","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":10,"verseStart":8,"chapterEnd":10,"verseEnd":8},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-10-13","title":"1 Samuel 10:13","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":10,"verseStart":13,"chapterEnd":10,"verseEnd":13},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-13-1","title":"1 Samuel 13:1–31:4","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":13,"verseStart":1,"chapterEnd":31,"verseEnd":4},"content":"<p><milestone</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-13-8","title":"1 Samuel 13:8","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":13,"verseStart":8,"chapterEnd":13,"verseEnd":8},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-14-26","title":"1 Samuel 14:26","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":14,"verseStart":26,"chapterEnd":14,"verseEnd":26},"content":"<p>windows of narrow lights Cf. 2 Chronicles 4:20. In the holy of holies in the tabernacle no light but the shekinah glory was provided. In many ways Solomon's temple manifests the spiritual deterioration of the people, and Jehovah's condescension to it in grace.</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-15-3","title":"1 Samuel 15:3","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":15,"verseStart":3,"chapterEnd":15,"verseEnd":3},"content":"<p>Bul Eighth month i.e. November.</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-15-6","title":"1 Samuel 15:6","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":15,"verseStart":6,"chapterEnd":15,"verseEnd":6},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-17-36","title":"1 Samuel 17:36","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":17,"verseStart":36,"chapterEnd":17,"verseEnd":36},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-20-11","title":"1 Samuel 20:11","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":20,"verseStart":11,"chapterEnd":20,"verseEnd":11},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-20-13","title":"1 Samuel 20:13","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":20,"verseStart":13,"chapterEnd":20,"verseEnd":13},"content":"<p>Rehoboam called Roboam. Matthew 1:7.</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-23-13","title":"1 Samuel 23:13","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":23,"verseStart":13,"chapterEnd":23,"verseEnd":13},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-23-25","title":"1 Samuel 23:25","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":23,"verseStart":25,"chapterEnd":23,"verseEnd":25},"content":"<p>high places Cf. 2 Chronicles 14:3. It appears that local sacrifices to Jehovah (though not according to the divine order) were offered in the times of the kings upon \"high places\" (cf) 1 Samuel 9:12. Apparently Asa's mother had defiled one of these with an idol, 1 Kings 15:13. Asa destroyed the idol and the idolatrous (but not the Jehovistic) \"high places.\" But see \"high places,\" (See Scofield \"1 Kings 3:2\") .</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-24-3","title":"1 Samuel 24:3","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":3,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":3},"content":"<p>type=\"x-importer\" subType=\"x-osis2mod\" n=\"$Rev: 3769 $ (SWORD: 1.9.0)\"/></p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-25-42","title":"1 Samuel 25:42","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":25,"verseStart":42,"chapterEnd":25,"verseEnd":42},"content":"<p>Obadiah In such a time as the reign of Ahab and Jezebel a believer's true place was by Elijah's side. Obadiah is a warning type of the men of God who adhere to the world while still seeking to serve God. The secret of the Lord, and the power of the Lord were with Elijah, the separated servant. Cf. 2 Timothy 2:20,21. feared (See Scofield \"Psalms 19:9\") .</p>"},{"id":"scofield-1sa-30-intro","title":"1 Samuel 30 — Chapter Introduction","author":"C. I. Scofield (1843–1921)","reference":{"book":"1SA","chapterStart":30,"verseStart":0,"chapterEnd":30,"verseEnd":0},"content":"<p>inner Heb. \"a chamber in a chamber.\" 1 Kings 22:25.</p>"}]}